        "text": "[accordion collapsed]\n\nKeynote Conversation - Kirsten Johnson and Amy Ziering\n\nDive into the work of a top doc DP in this illuminating and inspirational conversation and clips program.\n\n[/accordion][accordion collapsed]\n\nLunch / Exhibitor Visiting Time\n\nMingle, spend with time with our exhibitors, and enjoy a catered meal on AFI’s leafy outdoor patio.\n\n[/accordion][accordion collapsed]\n\nThe Hear and Now: Recording for the Best Location Sound Possible\n\nSeasoned audio mixers discuss the mics, accessories, and methods they use in recording broadcast quality interviews and verité.\n\n[/accordion][accordion collapsed]\n\nAdding Production Value and Shooting in Specialized Situations\n\nLearn how drones, image stabilizers, and sliders can add production value to your docs, then hear strategies used by top DPs shooting abroad, in harsh weather, low light, tight spaces and crowds.\n\n[/accordion][accordion collapsed]\n\n4K and Verité: Finding the Right Resolution -- Presented by Canon\n\nExpert DPs weigh in on the great resolution debate: how do you decide whether to shoot in HD, 2K, or 4K? Get their top tips for shooting docs across all resolutions.\n\n[/accordion]"
